	<li><a href="/en/money_and_tax/tax/capital_taxes/capital_acquisitions_tax.html">Capital Acquisitions Tax</a><br>If you receive a gift, you may have to pay gift tax on it. If you receive an inheritance following a death, it may be liable to inheritance tax. Both these taxes are types of Capital Acquisitions Tax.</li>
	
